  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_138",
    "english": "Among the orcs of the Demon Realm, one can be successful enough to take the place of a crime syndicate warlord. Because they have to focus on business operations, they don't usually dirty their hands, but sometimes they act directly, displaying their \"skills\" that made them a warlord.",
